name: Faux Pave Textured Gold Chain Bracelet
description:
Inspired by the Classic Pave Link Bracelet from J.Crew, this luxurious bracelet embodies timelessness and class. Oversize, champagne gold links with gold spring clasp. This bracelet, like our Chunky Gold Bracelet, fits snugly.

*Measure your wrist where you want the bracelet to fall and add half an inch. Pick the size closest to your number, and remember it is always best to round up.

XS- 6.5 in length (for petites) 
S - 7 in length 
M - 8 in length (standard)
L - 8.5 in length


See this bracelet and more in my Etsy shop: http://yunikelley.etsy.com

name: Crystal Brulee Bracelet
description:
Dress it up or dress it down! This classic crystal bracelet is inspired by tiny crème brûlée ramekins and is a sure staple piece in your jewelry collection. Faceted glass stones in brass ox settings.

PLEASE measure the circumference of your wrist where you want the bracelet to fall (usually 2-3 inches above the actual wrist). The bracelet will lie flat on your wrist so no additional wiggle room is required unless you want a loose fit. Hint: Loosely measure your wrist if you want a looser fit.

XS - 6.5 inches (pretty small)
S/M - 7 inches (small size or snug fit for a M)
L - 8 inches


See this bracelet and more in my Etsy shop: http://yunikelley.etsy.com

name: Crystal Pave Link Bracelet
description:
The bracelet that started it all, the Crystal Pave Link Bracelet is now available now at half the price of the original. Light gold base links studded with as many crystals that could fit for an intensely fiery sparkle in a gloriously chunky bracelet.

S - 8 inches
M - 8.5 inches (standard size)
L - 9 inches

name: Crystal Venus Flytrap Necklace
description:
A modern take on the 1930s Art Deco open-back crystal necklace: 18 circular glass stones enclosed in brass ox prong settings. Layer it for a bold, statement look. Necklace measures 22.5 inches including extender.

See this necklace and more in my Etsy shop: http://yunikelley.etsy.com

name: Rose Gold Pave Ball Clasp Bracelet
description:
This bracelet is as delightful as it is lovely! Chunky, rose gold links surround a sparkling rose gold magnetic clasp for seamless beauty and ease of wearing. Simply hold the two ends close and the strong magnets snap together! To take off, simply tug the bracelet and the magnets come right apart.

*Measure your wrist where you want the bracelet to fall and add an inch. Pick the size closest to your number, and remember it is always best to round up.

XS- 7 in length (for petites) 
S - 7.5 in length 
M - 8 in length (standard)
L - 8.5 in length


See this bracelet and more in my Etsy shop: http://yunikelley.etsy.com
